amitriptyline." Neuropsychobiology 15 (1986): 31-7[9] "Product Information. Rexulti (brexpiprazole)." Otsuka American Pharmaceuticals Inc, Rockville, MD.', 'Fluphenazine, Haloperidol, Thiothixene, Risperidone, Amisulpride, Quetiapine, Prochlorperazine, Promazine, Thioridazine, Lumateperone, Pimozide, More', 'Cyclosporine, Ustekinumab, Anifrolumab, Canakinumab, Secukinumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Anakinra, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, More', 1767369485);
